---

- When a new feature is requested, we must first illustrate the feature with a set of examples defined in Gherkin that serve as executable specifications of the feature.
- These gherkin examples are to be implemented first 
- Examples should include common scenarios as well as examples that illustrate complexity or risk.
- Use best practice gherkin such as using tables for various values. 
- Use behave python module 
